{"tid":2150548,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國財政部解除對澳門滙業銀行制裁","createTime":"2020-08-11T04:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T05:16:08.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8e4db82a0826cbeb4ebd12d65a04195eb3a8980e","tid":2150548,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T04:01:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543041-20200811.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543041-20200811.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lDkC3bY0i4P88JjHF8GLL0M%3D&h=f0b8346d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543041-20200811.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e6223051\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543041-20200811.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國財政部金融犯罪防制署撤銷對澳門滙業銀行的制裁，滙業財經集團主席區宗傑指，收到美國政府正式通知，在無需進一步訴訟，亦無任何一方須承認任何責任下，已正式解除自2005年起對滙業銀行的制裁。<br />\n<br />\n區宗傑指，有關決定不論對他個人或滙業銀行來說，均是重要的一步。滙業銀行承諾會致力消除監管機構及美國政府的疑慮，證明將來再沒有監管行動的需要，並期待就集團為打擊各種形式的洗錢活動所作的努力，與美國財政部金融犯罪防制署保持溝通。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，當時機成熟時，該行將恢復美元結算業務，並繼續發展私人銀行服務、資產管理、海外房地產業務，服務港澳及大灣區市民。<br />\n<br />\n滙業銀行在2005年被指涉嫌協助北韓客戶洗黑錢，美國財政部建議所有公司斷絕與銀行的聯繫。"},{"pid":"f01e12c284d08e8ae27f2781ecb6a57856b8229b","tid":2150548,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T04:02:16.000Z","msg":"提一提：<br />\n<br />\n美國財政部可以制裁成間銀行<br />\n<br />\n跟唔跟？自己諗"},{"pid":"12b49bc5da4cc5483aacf0ca0446d1c4772c0fa8","tid":2150548,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T04:02:18.000Z","msg":"可以做金融中心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b42a9b426007b7be89e209c8d6eba8ee10631a","tid":2150548,"uid":323228,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8e4db82a0826cbeb4ebd12d65a04195eb3a8980e","tid":2150548,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"